insert into [tbl_ArticleInfo]([ImportID],[Title],[ImportCatalog],[Note],[ImportPublicDate],[SerialNum]) select '252','关于召开市直机关党的群团工作会议的通知','通知','<p class="p1"><span class="s1">中共柳州市直属机关工作委员会</span></p><p class="p3"><span class="s2">柳直会通〔</span><span class="s3">2016</span><span class="s2">〕</span><span class="s3">14</span><span class="s2">号</span></p><p class="p5"><span class="s2">关于召开市直机关党的群团工作会议的通知</span></p><p class="p7"><span class="s2">市直机关各党组织：</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s4">为</span><span class="s2">深入学习贯彻中央党的群团工作会议精神，认真学习习近平总书记</span><span class="s5">在党的群团工作会议上的重要讲话，</span><span class="s2">总结经验、</span><span class="s5">表彰先进</span><span class="s2">，部署市直机关党的群团工作任务，经研究，决定召开市直机关党的群团工作会议。现将有关事项通知如下：</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s2">一、会议时间及地点</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">1</span><span class="s2">．会议时间：</span><span class="s3">2016</span><span class="s2">年</span><span class="s3">10</span><span class="s2">月</span><span class="s3">21</span><span class="s2">日（星期五）上午</span><span class="s3">9:00</span><span class="s2">（</span><span class="s3">8:45</span><span class="s2">前签到）。</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">2</span><span class="s2">．会议地点：市文昌会议中心一楼礼堂。</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s2">二、会议主要内容</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s3">1.</span><span class="s2">市直机关工青妇群团工作先进单位代表作经验介绍；</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s3">2.</span><span class="s2">表彰先进单位和个人；</span></p><p class="p10"><span class="s3">3.</span><span class="s2">为市直机关</span><span class="s3">“</span><span class="s2">相约榕树下</span><span class="s3">”</span><span class="s2">品牌十大文化俱乐部授牌；</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">4.</span><span class="s2">市委秘书长、市直机关工委书记崔峻同志讲话。</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s2">三、参加会议人员</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">1</span><span class="s2">．市直机关各部、委、办、局分管群团工作的领导</span><span class="s3">1</span><span class="s2">名；</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">2</span><span class="s2">．市直机关基层工会组织负责人</span><span class="s3">1</span><span class="s2">名；</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">3</span><span class="s2">．市直机关团工委管辖各共青团组织负责人</span><span class="s3">1</span><span class="s2">名；</span></p><p class="p8"><span class="s3">4</span><span class="s2">．市直机关各妇女组织负责人</span><span class="s3">1</span><span class="s2">名。</span></p><p class="p11"><span class="s6">请各单位填写与会人员回执单（附后），于</span><span class="s7">10</span><span class="s6">月</span><span class="s7">19</span><span class="s6">日下午</span><span class="s7">6:00</span><span class="s6">前通过市电子政务公文交换系统或传真报市直机关工委（电话：</span><span class="s7">2826986</span><span class="s6">，传真：</span><span class="s3">2616305</span><span class="s6">、</span><span class="s7">2867022</span><span class="s6">）。</span><span class="s2">会议重要，</span><span class="s6">如需请假要按规定办理请假手续，报市直机关工委按程序审批。</span></p><p class="p13"><span class="s3"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span></span><span class="s2">附件：参加市直机关党的群团工作会议人员回执表</span></p><p class="p15"><span class="s2">中共柳州市直属机关工作委员会</span></p><p class="p16"><span class="s2">２０１６年１０月１７日</span></p><p class="p18"><span class="s2">（网络传输）</span></p><p class="p19"><span class="s2">附件</span><span class="s9">:</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s2">参加市直机关党的群团工作会议人员回执表</span></p><p class="p23"><span class="s2">单位（盖章）：</span></p><table class="t1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td class="td1" valign="top"></td><td class="td2" valign="top"><p class="p26"><span class="s2">姓名</span></p></td><td class="td3" valign="top"><p class="p26"><span class="s2">职务</span></p></td><td class="td4" valign="top"><p class="p26"><span class="s2">备注</span></p></td></tr><tr><td class="td5" valign="top"><p class="p26"><span class="s2">分管群团工作的领导</span></p></td><td class="td6" valign="top"></td><td class="td7" valign="top"></td><td class="td8" valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td class="td1" valign="top"><p class="p26"><span class="s2">工会组织负责人</span></p></td><td class="td2" valign="top"></td><td class="td3" valign="top"></td><td class="td4" valign="top"></td></