1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">”</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1">二、活动内容</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1">（一）举办</span><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年市直机关干部职工庆祝建党</span><span class="s8">95</span><span class="s1">周年</span><span class="s8">“</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">朗诵比赛</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1">（二）举办</span><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年市直机关干部职工庆祝建党</span><span class="s8">95</span><span class="s1">周年</span><span class="s8">“</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">征文比赛</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1">三、活动时间</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年</span><span class="s8">6</span><span class="s1">月中旬</span><span class="s8">―7</span><span class="s1">月中旬（具体活动时间详见方案）</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1">四、活动要求</span></p><p class="p10"><span class="s1"><b>（一）领导重视，积极参与。</b>在市直机关范围内开展庆祝建党</span><span class="s8">95</span><span class="s1">周年</span><span class="s8">“</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">系列活动，目的是为了让机关广大干部职工进一步抒发热爱祖国、热爱党的真情实感，丰富干部职工的业余文化生活，促进各单位、机关各部门间的交流。各单位要高度重视，切实做好宣传发动，积极组织报名参赛。</span></p><p class="p10"><span class="s1"><b>（二）相互学习，增进友谊。</b>系列活动分为朗诵和征文两种文化形式，充分展现市直机关干部职工的风采、展现别样的精神面貌，希望各单位借此平台，相互学习，增进友谊，为建设</span><span class="s8">“</span><span class="s1">五美五好</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">柳州做贡献。各单位也可先期在本单位范围内开展相关活动选拔赛，再做推荐。</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1"><b>（三）详读方案，踊跃报名。</b>请各单位详读活动方案，积极组织报名，严格按时间节点报送相关材料及人员名单。</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s1">联系人：李鹏飞</span><span class="s8"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span></span><span class="s1">联系电话：</span><span class="s8">2826986</span></p><p class="p12"><span class="s1">附件：</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s8">1.2016</span><span class="s1">年市直机关干部职工庆祝建党</span><span class="s8">95</span><span class="s1">周年</span><span class="s8">“</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">朗诵比赛方案</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s8">2.2016</span><span class="s1">年市直机关干部职工庆祝建党</span><span class="s8">95</span><span class="s1">周年</span><span class="s8">“</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">征文比赛方案</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s8">3.</span><span class="s1">朗诵比赛评分标准</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s8">4.</span><span class="s1">朗诵比赛报名表</span></p><p class="p9"><span class="s8">5.</span><span class="s1">征文比赛报名表</span></p><p class="p14"><span class="s1">柳州市直属机关工会工作委员会</span></p><p class="p15"><span class="s1">2016</span><span class="s9">年</span><span class="s1">5</span><span class="s9">月</span><span class="s1">31</span><span class="s9">日</span></p><p class="p16"><span class="s8">(</span><span class="s1">网络传输</span><span class="s8">)</span></p><p class="p17"><span class="s10">附件</span><span class="s1">1:</span></p><p class="p19"><span class="s7">2016</span><span class="s1">年市直机关干部职工庆祝建党</span><span class="s7">95</span><span class="s1">周年</span></p><p class="p19"><span class="s7">“</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s7">”</span><span class="s1">朗诵比赛方案</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">一、参赛名额、资格</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">每单位限报一名参赛选手，选手必须是本单位在职在编的干部职工。</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">二、主题要求</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">朗诵篇目题材应为中华经典诗文，篇目内容要求健康向上、催人进取，能够表现爱国、爱党情感、民族性，体现中华优秀传统文化，具有正确的价值导向作用。</span></p><p class="p22"><span class="s1">三、朗诵形式</span></p><p class="p22"><span class="s1">形式可多样，单人、小组、集体朗诵均可，可配乐，背景音乐自行准备。</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">四、比赛时间、地点</span></p><p class="p23"><span class="s1">（一）时间：</span><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年</span><span class="s8">6</span><span class="s1">月</span><span class="s8">21</span><span class="s1">日。</span></p><p class="p23"><span class="s1">（二）地点：待领队会上另行通知。</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">五、评选与奖励</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">（一）初赛评出一等奖</span><span class="s8">2</span><span class="s1">名、二等奖</span><span class="s8">4</span><span class="s1">名、三等奖</span><span class="s8">6</span><span class="s1">名、优秀奖</span><span class="s8">10</span><span class="s1">名。</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">（二）决赛评出特等奖</span><span class="s8">1</span><span class="s1">名、一等奖</span><span class="s8">2</span><span class="s1">名、二等奖</span><span class="s8">3</span><span class="s1">名、三等奖</span><span class="s8">4</span><span class="s1">名、优秀奖若干名。</span></p><p class="p21"><span class="s1">六、要求</span></p><p class="p24"><span class="s1">（一）组织专家评委现场打分，朗诵者必须脱稿，朗诵时间</span><span class="s8">3―5</span><span class="s1">分钟，超时扣分。本次比赛不设背景屏幕及投影。比赛时，参赛各单位均可派出最多</span><span class="s8">5</span><span class="s1">人观赛助阵。</span></p><p class="p24"><span class="s1">（二）领队会定于</span><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年</span><span class="s8">6</span><span class="s1">月</span><span class="s8">20</span><span class="s1">日</span><span class="s8">15:30</span><span class="s1">分</span><span class="s8">,</span><span class="s1">在市文昌综合楼七楼</span><span class="s8">741</span><span class="s1">会议室召开。领队会将进行比赛顺序抽签，请参赛单位领队务必提前</span><span class="s8">20</span><span class="s1">分钟按时参加。</span></p><p class="p24"><span class="s1">（三）请各单位认真推选参赛选手，充分展现单位文化实力。朗诵篇目、配乐（</span><span class="s8">mp3</span><span class="s1">格式）及比赛报名表电子版，务必于</span><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年</span><span class="s8">6</span><span class="s1">月</span><span class="s8">10</span><span class="s1">日前报市直机关工会工委邮箱（</span><span class="s8">lzjggh@163.com</span><span class="s1">），投</span><span class="s11">稿</span><span class="s1">请注明</span><span class="s8">“‘</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">’</span><span class="s1">朗诵比赛</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">字样，逾期不再接受补报。</span></p><p class="p25"><span class="s9">联系人：李鹏飞</span><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span></span><span class="s9">联系电