12"><span class="s1">七、投稿方式</span></p><p class="p30"><span class="s1">请各单位认真推选参赛作品，充分展现单位文化实力。于</span><span class="s8">2016</span><span class="s1">年</span><span class="s8">6</span><span class="s1">月</span><span class="s8">20</span><span class="s1">日前将作品一式三份（纸制版作品不写作者，在作品题目左侧加盖单位公章。）连同电子版报市直机关工会工委邮箱（</span><span class="s8">lzjggh@163.com</span><span class="s1">），投稿请注明</span><span class="s8">“‘</span><span class="s1">迎风飘扬的旗帜</span><span class="s8">’</span><span class="s1">征文比赛</span><span class="s8">”</span><span class="s1">字样，逾期不再接受补报。</span></p><p class="p31"><span class="s9">联系人：李鹏飞</span><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span></span><span class="s9">联系电话：</span><span class="s1">2826986 </span></p><p class="p33"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">             </span></span></p><p class="p34"><span class="s10">附件</span><span class="s1">3:</span></p><p class="p35"><span class="s1">朗诵比赛评分标准</span></p><table class="t1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td class="td1" valign="middle"><p class="p37"><span class="s1"><b>评分指标</b></span></p><p class="p38"><span class="s1"><b>（总分</b></span><span class="s5"><b>10</b></span><span class="s12"><b>分）</b></span></p></td><td class="td2" valign="middle"><p class="p39"><span class="s12"><b>评</b></span><span class="s1"><b><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span></b></span><span class="s12"><b>分</b></span><span class="s1"><b><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span></b></span><span class="s12"><b>标</b></span><span class="s1"><b><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span></b></span><span class="s12"><b>准</b></span></p></td></tr><tr><td class="td3" valign="middle"><p class="p37"><span class="s1"><b>主题内容</b></span></p><p class="p37"><span class="s10"><b>（</b></span><span class="s5"><b>2</b></span><span class="s1"><b>分）</b></span></p></td><td class="td4" valign="middle"><p class="p40"><span class="s1">朗诵内容符合本次比赛要求，突出主题，健康向上，思想性、艺术性强</span></p></td></tr><tr><td class="td1" vali